{"word":"Teraphim","slug":"teraphim","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Teraphim</b> Household idols.<br/> Used by Laban, stolen by Rachel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=19'>Gen 31:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=35'>Gen 31:35</a><br/> Used by Micah, stolen by the Danites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=17&verse=5'>Jdg 17:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=18&verse=14'>Jdg 18:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=18&verse=20'>Jdg 18:20</a><br/> Condemned and disposed of by Jacob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=4'>Gen 35:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=39'>Gen 31:39</a><br/> Destroyed by Josiah<br/> <a href='S:Idol'>Idol</a>"}]}